Erayga Endothermic wuxuu qeexayaa habka ama jawaab celin(rogaal celinata), taas oo nidaamka oo ka nuuga tamarta laga bilaabo ku hareeraysan ee foomka kulaylka. Ereyga mujiaahidiintii Marcellin Berthelot oo ka baxay jiriddii ay Giriig ah endo-, oo ka soo jeeda erayga "endon" (ἔνδον) oo macnihiisu yahay "gudahood" iyo "therm" xididka (θερμ-) oo macnihiisu yahay "u kulul." Dareen The loogu talo galay waa in of cadaanyo in ku xiran tahay qaadanaya kulaylka haddii ay tahay in la sii wado. Tirada ka soo horjeeda geedi socodka ah endothermic waa nidaam exothermic, mid ka mid ah in releases, "siinayaa baxay" tamarta ee foomka kulaylka. Sidaas oo in muddo dheer kasta (endothermic & exothermic) horgalaha jeedaa meesha kulaylka keliyo falcelinta dhacdaa.
